  "prompt": "Does Mi4i has SD card slot?",
  "response": "Yes, the Xiaomi Mi4i **does** have a microSD card slot. This allows you to expand the device's storage capacity beyond the internal memory provided. Typically, the Mi4i supports microSD cards up to **32GB**, enabling you to store more photos, videos, apps, and other data without worrying about running out of space.\n\n**Key Points:**\n- **Expandable Storage:** The Mi4i includes a dedicated microSD card slot.\n- **Supported Capacity:** It generally supports microSD cards up to 32GB.\n- **Accessibility:** The microSD slot is usually located next to the SIM card slot, allowing for dual SIM and expandable storage configurations.\n\nIf you're planning to purchase a microSD card for your Mi4i, ensure it's a reputable brand and within the supported capacity to guarantee compatibility and optimal performance.",
